Class Aula

java.lang.Object
model.Aula
All Implemented Interfaces:
AulaInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
AulaDidattica, Laboratorio
public abstract class Aula extends Object implements AulaInterface
Represents an abstract classroom with basic properties such as number, capacity, and type. This class serves as a base for specific classroom types implementing AulaInterface.

    • getAccessori

      public abstract Object getAccessori()
      Retrieves the accessories available in the classroom.

      This method must be implemented by concrete subclasses to return the specific accessories appropriate to their type (e.g., EnumSet<AccessorioDidattica> for didactic classrooms or EnumSet<AccessorioLaboratorio> for laboratories).

      Specified by:
      getAccessori in interface AulaInterface
      Returns:
